Subject: drm/xe/guc: Adding steering info support for GuC register lists
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 64192bb2e52d48cfccd8373b0ad565bb9ce3d2e6
